{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"完了 (かんりょう — done)! Here's what I implemented:\n\n**JEM-71 — Project list view:**\n\n- **API layer**: Added `Project` type with `name`, `status`, `lead`, `progress`, `url` fields. Added `fetch_projects()` (via team memberships with dedup) and `fetch_project_issues()` to the `LinearApi` trait, `LinearClient`, and `FakeLinearApi`.\n- **App state**: Added project list (`ProjectList`) and project detail (`ProjectDetail`) views with full Vim navigation (`j/k/g/G/Enter/Esc`), caching, and refresh support.\n- **Views**: Created `project_list.rs` (table with Name/Status/Lead/Progress columns, color-coded) and `project.rs` (issues within a selected project with ID/Title/Status/Priority/Assignee).\n- **Key binding**: `p` switches to project list from My Issues; `Enter` drills into project issues; `Esc` navigates back. Added to help overlay.\n- **Tests**: 28 new tests (173 total) covering navigation, view switching, caching, API fetching, type deserialization, and key mapping."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":493,"cache_read_input_tokens":119855,"output_tokens":288,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff7e-e369-77bd-9b4c-f08017c4f46c"}
